Consort diagram for potential DILT1D study participants registered on the DILT1D database until the point of treatment. The most successful method of registering potential participants was via self-referral from the study website (internet). Once individuals registered with the study team, similar proportions from each source proceeded to trial enrolment. Participants who were negative for autoantibodies were from the clinics (N = 2), internet (N = 2) and register (N = 1) (not permitted - outside the EU or registered after last participant treated, non-communicators - initially registered but did not respond to messages from DILT1D team).Table 3
